08:29:27.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 一切反動派都是紙老虎。看起來，反動派的樣子是可怕的，但是實際上並沒有什麽了不起的力量。從長遠的觀點看問題，真正強大的力量不是屬於反動派，而是屬於人民。<br />\n<br />\n 革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫綉花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。革命是暴動，是一個階級推翻另一個階級的暴烈的行動。<br />\n哪裏有壓迫，哪裏就有反抗<br />\n<br />\n世界是你們的，也是我們的，但是歸根結底是你們的。你們年青人朝氣蓬勃，正在興旺時候，好像早晨八、九點鍾的太陽。希望寄托在你們身上。"},{"pid":"46e3b8536f77001fa64ff04f6674835956b20cd6","tid":1998151,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caddef26322fdfaf5593c38402c0df9dbe43223c","tid":1998151,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d3a42550a2c9ca3b385efde43957f916a45e176","tid":1998151,"uid":137053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:27:32.000Z","msg":"想知中聯辦除咗發聲明仲有識做咩？<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦咁多錢買香港物業，唔支持藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:28:47.000Z","msg":"干預區會＋立會選舉<br />\n干預地區組織<br />\n干預1200人小圈子<br />\n買地自肥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"偽愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb336d0a3aca98407f93196925c95e7c299db598","tid":1998151,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"叫班差佬幫襯紅色經濟圈頂住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceeb63ced0f8a57c953764834b3d817498eba3f5","tid":1998151,"uid":21761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa7419e8a222c14f133093c8e637c2f67d2b274","tid":1998151,"uid":1108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cd143a933ff5ac9543537051153fb736fdd0f96","ti